# Formatting & Linting

## Tools
- ESLint + Prettier for both backend (`src/`) and frontend (`src/ui/`).
- Run linting before committing.

## Communication Style
- Be concise. No essays, no long explanations, no meta commentary.
- State what changed and why in one line if needed.
